@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zymesx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v1 + 1.00) / (v1 + 0.34 + v1 + 0.47)))
    v0 = (v1 - wp.sin(0.42))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = wp.sin(v0)
    v1 = (wp.sin(v0) * wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.20)))
    v2 = (((v0 + 0.02 / v0 + 0.82) + wp.cos(v1 + 0.61)) - (v2 - 0.30))
    tmp = (0.80 - (0.68 / (tmp + 0.29 + tmp + 0.34)))
    data[tid] = v0
